   "source": [
    "from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\n",
    "X=df.iloc[:,0:11].values\n",
    "y=df.iloc[:,11].values\n",
    "\n",
    "X_train,X_test,y_train,y_test = train_test_split(X,y,random_state=40,stratify=y,test_size=0.2)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 47,
   "id": "b6063b6e",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler\n",
    "\n",
    "std = StandardScaler()\n",
    "std.fit(X_train)\n",
    "X_train_std = std.transform(X_train)\n",
    "X_test_std=std.transform(X_test)"
   ]
  },

   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Decision Tree"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",

   "source": [
    "from sklearn.tree import DecisionTreeClassifier\n",
    "from sklearn.model_selection import GridSearchCV\n",
    "\n",
    "decision_tree_gini = DecisionTreeClassifier(criterion=\"gini\")\n",
    "decision_tree_entropy = DecisionTreeClassifier(criterion=\"entropy\")\n",
    "decision_tree_log = DecisionTreeClassifier(criterion=\"log_loss\")\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "param_grid = {\n",
    "    'max_depth': [None, 10, 20, 30, 40, 50],  \n",
    "    'min_samples_split': [2, 5, 10],  \n",
    "    'min_samples_leaf': [1, 2, 4]  \n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "grid_search_gini = GridSearchCV(estimator=decision_tree_gini, param_grid=param_grid, cv=5, verbose=2, n_jobs=-1)\n",
    "grid_search_gini.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"Best parameters for Decision Tree with gini:\")\n",
    "print(grid_search_gini.best_params_)\n",
    "\n",
    "grid_search_entophy = GridSearchCV(estimator=decision_tree_entropy, param_grid=param_grid, cv=5, verbose=2, n_jobs=-1)\n",
    "grid_search_entophy.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"Best parameters for Decision Tree with Entropy:\")\n",
    "print(grid_search_entophy.best_params_)\n",
    "\n",
    "grid_search_log = GridSearchCV(estimator=decision_tree_log, param_grid=param_grid, cv=5, verbose=2, n_jobs=-1)\n",
    "grid_search_log.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"Best parameters for Decision Tree with Log Loss:\")\n",
    "print(grid_search_log.best_params_)"
   ]

    "from sklearn.preprocessing import OneHotEncoder\n",
    "\n",
    "categorical_columns = df_renamed.select_dtypes(include=['object']).columns.tolist()\n",
    "\n",
    "encoder = OneHotEncoder(sparse_output=False)\n",
    "\n",
    "one_hot_encoded = encoder.fit_transform(df_renamed[categorical_columns])\n",
    "\n",
    "one_hot_df = pd.DataFrame(one_hot_encoded, columns=encoder.get_feature_names_out(categorical_columns))\n",
    "\n",
    "df_encoded = pd.concat([df_renamed, one_hot_df], axis=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "df_encoded = df_encoded.drop(categorical_columns, axis=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"Encoded Employee data : \\n{df_encoded}\")\n"
   ]

    "from sklearn.tree import DecisionTreeClassifier\n",
    "from sklearn.model_selection import GridSearchCV\n",

    "decision_tree_gini = DecisionTreeClassifier(criterion=\"gini\")\n",

    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "grid_search_gini = GridSearchCV(estimator=decision_tree_gini, param_grid=param_grid, cv=5, verbose=2, n_jobs=-1)\n",
    "grid_search_gini.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"Best parameters for Decision Tree with gini:\")\n",
    "print(grid_search_gini.best_params_)\n",
    "\n",
    "grid_search_entophy = GridSearchCV(estimator=decision_tree_entropy, param_grid=param_grid, cv=5, verbose=2, n_jobs=-1)\n",
    "grid_search_entophy.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"Best parameters for Decision Tree with Entropy:\")\n",
    "print(grid_search_entophy.best_params_)\n",
    "\n",
    "grid_search_log = GridSearchCV(estimator=decision_tree_log, param_grid=param_grid, cv=5, verbose=2, n_jobs=-1)\n",
    "grid_search_log.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"Best parameters for Decision Tree with Log Loss:\")\n",
    "print(grid_search_log.best_params_)"
